{"name":"Grendelle the Grotesque","size":"medium","type":"fey","tag":"Hag","alignment":"neutral evil","hitDice":"15","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":5,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (natural armor)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"15","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"112 (15d8 + 45)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"18","dexPoints":"15","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"16","wisPoints":"14","chaPoints":"16","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"6","customCr":"3 (700 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"","isLair":true,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, Grendelle can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), Grendelle can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The grapple action may not happen two turns in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the green hag's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the green hag's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the green hag dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Amphibious","desc":"[MON] can breathe air and water."},{"name":"Magic Resistance","desc":"[MON] has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects."},{"name":"Mimicry","desc":"[MON] can mimic animal sounds and humanoid voices. A creature that hears the sounds can tell they are imitations with a successful DC 14 Wisdom (Insight) check."},{"name":"Innate Spellcasting","desc":"[MON]'s innate spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC [CHA SAVE]). She can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:\n\n\n> At will: _Dancing lights, Minor Illusion, Vicious Mockery,\n           Grease , Magic Mouth_\n> 4/day: _Charm Person, Ray of Sickness, Sleep_\n> 3/day: _See Invisibility, Locate Object, Ray of Enfeeblement_\n> 2/day: _Major Image, Antagonize, Thunder Step (trident)_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Claws","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 13 (2d8 + 4) slashing damage."},{"name":"Illusory Appearance","desc":"[MON] covers herself and anything she is wearing or carrying with a magical illusion that makes her look like another creature of her general size and humanoid shape. The illusion ends if the hag takes a bonus action to end it or if she dies.\nThe changes wrought by this effect fail to hold up to physical inspection. For example, the hag could appear to have smooth skin, but someone touching her would feel her rough flesh. Otherwise, a creature must take an action to visually inspect the illusion and succeed on a DC 20 Intelligence (Investigation) check to discern that the hag is disguised."},{"name":"Invisible Passage","desc":"[MON] magically turns invisible until she attacks or casts a spell, or until her concentration ends (as if concentrating on a spell). While invisible, she leaves no physical evidence of her passage, so she can be tracked only by magic. Any equipment she wears or carries is invisible with her."},{"name":"Seaspray Threespear","desc":"The trident booms with the crashing of waves and any creature within a 30ft cone must make a DC 14 constitution save or be deafened and charmed for a minute. While charmed, the creature is incapacitated and can't move. If the creature takes damage, or succeeds on a DC 12 wisdom save at the end of it's turn, the charm ends, though the deafen does not"}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Greater Healing Potion (2)","desc":"[MON] drinks a potion and heals [4d4+4] hit points."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Misty Escape","desc":"Upon taking damage from an attack [Mon] may turn invisble and teleport up to 40ft."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int"},{"name":"deception","stat":"cha"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"poisoned"}],"languages":[{"name":"Abyssal","speaks":true},{"name":"Aire","speaks":true},{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Deep Speech","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Grendelle","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":4,"damage":[]}